    <section id="how">
      <h2 class="section-title">How it works</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Keep this tight. If your product needs a long explanation, the page will leak attention.</p>
      <div class="cards">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>1) One-sentence promise</h3>
          <p>Say what the user gets. Avoid internal jargon.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>2) Three benefits</h3>
          <p>Make them measurable or concrete: time saved, risk reduced, clarity gained.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>3) Single action</h3>
          <p>Waitlist, demo request, or purchase. Don’t split attention.</p>
